<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="h-100">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - GoSix – Đi nhanh, sống trọn</title>

    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="~/css/images/icon_logo.png" type="image/x-icon" />
    <link rel="icon" href="~/css/images/icon_logo.png" type="image/png" />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" asp-append-version="true" />

    <style>
        body {
            background: url('https://img1.kienthucvui.vn/uploads/2021/01/13/phong-canh-thun-lung-bac-son-viet-nam-dep-nhu-tranh-ve_030119832.jpg') no-repeat center center fixed;
            background-size: cover;
            padding-top: 130px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        main {
            flex: 1 0 auto;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #212529 !important;
            color: #adb5bd;
            padding: 30px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .footer-section h5 {
            color: white;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .footer-section ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

            .footer-section ul li {
                margin-bottom: 8px;
            }

                .footer-section ul li a {
                    color: #adb5bd;
                    text-decoration: none;
                    transition: color 0.2s;
                }

                    .footer-section ul li a:hover {
                        color: white;
                    }

        .dangky-logo {
            max-width: 120px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .footer-bottom {
            border-top: 1px solid #495057;
            padding-top: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .nav-item {
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding-left: 25px;
            padding-right: 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        select {
            padding: 8px;
            width: 120px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border: none;
            background-color: orange;
            appearance: none;
        }

            select:hover {
                cursor: pointer;
                text-decoration: underline;
                color: white;
                font-weight: bold;
            }

            select:focus {
                outline: none;
                border: none;
            }

        .username-text {
            color: black;
            font-size: 18px;
            padding: 8px;
        }

            .username-text:hover {
                color: white;
                font-weight: bold;
                text-decoration: underline;
            }
        /* Vùng chứa user info */
        .nav-user {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

            /* Chữ "Xin chào + Username" */
            .nav-user .user-name {
                font-size: 18px;
                font-weight: 600;
                color: #ffffff !important;
                transition: 0.3s;
            }

                /* Hover icon + chữ */
                .nav-user .user-name:hover {
                    color: #fff200 !important;
                    text-shadow: 0 0 6px #fff200, 0 0 12px #ff9900;
                    transform: scale(1.05);
                }

        /* Dropdown menu item */
        .dropdown-glow .dropdown-item {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

            /* Hover item dropdown */
            .dropdown-glow .dropdown-item:hover {
                background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
                color: #fff200 !important;
            }

        /* Biểu tượng avatar */
        .user-icon {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-right: 6px;
        }

        /* Navbar Background Glow */
        .navbar-glow {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffdd00, #FF9900, #ffdd00);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 110, 0, 0.5);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        /* Logo hover effect */
        .logo-glow {
            padding-left:20%;
            height: 45px;
            transition: transform 0.3s, filter 0.3s;
        }

            .logo-glow:hover {
                transform: scale(1.1);
                filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px #fff200);
            }

        .logo-text-glow {
            color: white;
            text-shadow: 0 0 5px #fff200, 0 0 10px #ff6a00;
            font-size: 22px;
        }

        /* Menu items */
        .nav-glow {
            padding-right:20%;
            color: white !important;
            font-weight: 600;
            position: relative;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

            .nav-glow::after {
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                width: 0;
                height: 2px;
                left: 0;
                bottom: -3px;
                background: #ffdd00;
                transition: width 0.3s;
            }

            .nav-glow:hover::after {
                width: 100%;
            }

            .nav-glow:hover {
                color: #fff200 !important; /* neon yellow hover */
                text-shadow: 0 0 6px #fff200, 0 0 12px #ff9900;
                transform: scale(1.05);
            }

        /* Dropdown menu glow */
        .dropdown-glow {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ff6a00, #ffdd00);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255,110,0,0.5);
        }

            .dropdown-glow .dropdown-item:hover {
                background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
                color: white;
            }

        /* Buttons Neon */
        .btn-neon {
            background: #ff6a00;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 25px;
            padding: 6px 18px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

            .btn-neon:hover {
                box-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffdd00, 0 0 30px #ff6a00;
                transform: scale(1.05);
            }
    </style>

    @await RenderSectionAsync("Styles", required: false)
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg fixed-top py-3 navbar-glow">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <a class="navbar-brand d-flex align-items-center" asp-controller="Home_User" asp-action="Home_User">
                    <img src="~/css/images/logo_web.png" alt="GoSix" class="logo-glow" />
                </a>

                <button class="navbar-toggler border-0" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarContent"
                        aria-controls="navbarContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>

                <div class="collapse navbar-collapse text-center" id="navbarContent">

                    @if (User.Identity.IsAuthenticated)
                    {
                        @if (User.IsInRole("Admin"))
                        {
                            <ul class="navbar-nav mx-auto gap-4">
                                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link nav-glow"asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">Thống kê</a></li>
                                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link nav-glow" asp-controller="Home_User" asp-action="ChuyenXe_User">Lịch trình</a></li>
                                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link nav-glow" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home_User" asp-action="About">Về chúng tôi</a></li>
                                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link nav-glow" asp-area="" asp-controller="Chat" asp-action="Index">Liên hệ</a></li>

                            </ul>
                        }
                        else if (User.IsInRole("KhachHang"))
                        {
                            <ul class="navbar-nav mx-auto gap-4">
                                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link nav-glow" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home_User" asp-action="Home_User">Trang chủ</a></li>
                                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link nav-glow" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home_User" asp-action="PurchaseHistory">Lịch sử</a></li>
                                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link nav-glow" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home_User" asp-action="ChuyenXe_User">Lịch trình</a></li>
                                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link nav-glow" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home_User" asp-action="About">Về chúng tôi</a></li>
                                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link nav-glow" asp-area="" asp-controller="Chat" asp-action="Index">Liên hệ</a></li>
                            </ul>
                        }
                    }
                    else
                    {
                        <ul class="navbar-nav mx-auto gap-4">
                            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link nav-glow" asp-controller="Home_User" asp-action="Home_User">Trang chủ</a></li>
                            <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link nav-glow" asp-controller="Home_User" asp-action="About">Về chúng tôi</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    }


                    <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                        @if (User.Identity.IsAuthenticated)
                        {
                            <li class="nav-item dropdown nav-user">
                                <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle user-name" href="#" id="userDropdown" role="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">
                                    <i class="bi bi-person-circle user-icon"></i> Xin chào @User.Identity.Name
                                </a>
                                <ul class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-end dropdown-glow text-center">
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="Auth" asp-action="Account">Thông tin tài khoản</a></li>
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="Auth" asp-action="Logout">Đăng xuất</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                        }
                        else
                        {
                            <li class="nav-item d-flex gap-2">
                                <a class="btn btn-neon text-white" asp-controller="Auth" asp-action="Login">Đăng nhập</a>
                                <a class="btn btn-neon text-white" asp-controller="Auth" asp-action="Register">Đăng ký</a>
                            </li>
                        }
                    </ul>

                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>

    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <main role="main" class="pb-3">
            @RenderBody()
        </main>
    </div>

    <footer class="bg-dark text-white pt-4 pb-4">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row pb-4">
                <div class="col-6 col-md-3 footer-section">
                    <h5>GOSIX - Đi nhanh, Sống trọn</h5>
                    <img src="~/css/images/logo_web.png" alt="Đăng ký Logo" class="dangky-logo" />
                </div>

                <div class="col-6 col-md-3 footer-section">
                    <h5>Thông tin</h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="#" class="text-decoration-none">Điều khoản & Điều kiện</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="text-decoration-none">Chính sách bảo mật</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="text-decoration-none">Quy chế</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="col-6 col-md-3 footer-section mt-3 mt-md-0">
                    <h5>Về GoSix</h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="#" class="text-decoration-none">Về chúng tôi</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="text-decoration-none">Liên hệ</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="col-6 col-md-3 footer-section mt-3 mt-md-0">
                    <h5>Đặt</h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="#" class="text-decoration-none">Nhà Xe Limousine</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-bottom">
                <div class="row align-items-end">
                    <div class="col-12 col-lg-9 text-start">
                        <p class="mb-1">
                            Công ty TNHH GoSix Việt Nam<br />
                            Email: <a href="mailto:contact@gosix.vn" class="text-decoration-none text-white-50">contact@gosix.vn</a> | Liên hệ: **1900999999**
                        </p>
                        <p class="mb-1">
                            Địa chỉ văn phòng: Tầng 6 và 7, Tòa nhà Mê Linh Point, Số 2 Ngô Đức Kế, Phường Bến Nghé, Quận 1, Thành phố Hồ Chí Minh
                        </p>
                        <p class="mb-2">
                            Số Giấy chứng nhận đăng ký kinh doanh: 0317772069 được cấp bởi Sở Kế hoạch đầu tư Thành phố Hồ Chí Minh lần đầu ngày 4/6/2023.
                        </p>
                        <p class="mb-0 text-white-50">
                            &copy; 2025 GoSix Vietnam All Rights Reserved
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="~/lib/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="~/js/site.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
    @await RenderSectionAsync("Scripts", required: false)
</body>
</html>